metadata.name: Lilith
metadata.description:
Lilith (from Judaic mythology) who has always been depicted as the cunning figure while ignoring the softer image of her as the first wife of Adam. The idea behind this piece was to show her both vile and gentle side.

Photographer/Artist: Annie Ali

NFT holder can use this NFT in any form as they aspire to as long as creator is credited. (Copyright will always remain to the creator)
